# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ssdlc-action — Trivy accepted-risk list
#
# These CVEs are in the Go standard library embedded inside third-party
# binary tools shipped in the ssdlc-action Docker image (Gitleaks, Trivy, gh).
# They are NOT in ssdlc-action application code.
#
# Root cause: Go stdlib CVEs fixed in Go 1.24.13 / 1.25.7 (Feb 2026).
# Blocked on: upstream tools rebuilding with the patched Go toolchain.
#   - Gitleaks v8.30.0 — latest release as of 2026-03-02, built pre-fix
#   - Trivy / gh — from vendor apt repos, pending their Go toolchain updates
#
# Action: Remove each entry once the owning tool ships a release built with
#         Go ≥ 1.24.13 or ≥ 1.25.7, and re-confirm clean scan.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

